  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical study is to evaluate the safety of OPC-262 (2.5 mg and 5 mg) in
      patients with type 2 diabetes by long-term administration orally for 52 weeks and to evaluate
      the efficacy of OPC-262
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
